main event: A witness reported seeing three strange blinking lights in August 1963 over Syracuse, New York.
interesting points: The witness described the lights as crossing the path of an aircraft in flight,The sighting was reported to the Air Defense Command Headquarters,The project analysis concluded there was insufficient data for evaluation,No official UFO report was received from the Air Force regarding the sighting,The witness has a background in writing and has collected numerous UFO reports.
witness description: a civilian who has shown interest in UFO sightings and has a background in writing
